data.name: Label1.Text
data.value: Arellano University – Andres Bonifacio Campus provides quality elementary education focused on academic excellence, character formation, and holistic development of young learners. As part of the Arellano University system, the campus offers a safe, child-friendly, and supportive learning environment guided by qualified teachers, strong core values, and a commitment to accessible and affordable education, helping students build a solid foundation for future learning.
